{"tid":1519721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【831】Endgame你老母","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:23:06.000Z","uid":125508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"72e090b2bd9d16a322a3bf7ca2bd619db7e772d4","tid":1519721,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"臨大事，有靜氣。政府抓捕泛民議員，想嚇怕市民。你明天不出來，就反證了泛民議員就是你的大台：&ldquo;泛民一進你進，泛民一退你退&rdquo;。<br />\n明天831沒有泛民，行街購物買野，隨心所欲就得，不用大陣象做事，也不需要製造恐怖氣氛，說甚麼&ldquo;Endgame&rdquo;。<br />\n現在Endgame了嗎？為甚麼自己要定死線？現在自己要死了嗎？還是政府想速速了事？如果政府要速速了事，你要呼應，自亂陣腳，隨風起舞嗎？<br />\n謹記毛澤東名言：<span style=\"color: red;\">敵進我退，敵退我追</span><br />\n現在只是中局，往後還有大把野玩，香港人要有信心，常懷希望。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不是Endgame，是UP YOUR GAME</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d92ba457a828dca2336871ce8eb0c42dc950b89c","tid":1519721,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求入來推po！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士請快D碌入來！！！ 更新了整合名單，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1518567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1518567</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2dc07c32708bb2a9220872818a88745612a80404","tid":1519721,"uid":182827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:48:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">港共政府想玩攬炒，我地就要同佢地繼續玩落去</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8.31 START GAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"2112f4d85eae8af36b210